- **NEUTRAL**: Both sides equally valid.
- Check the "Structural Bias (Higher Timeframe)" field in your data and factor it into every decision.

### 7. WHEN NOT TO TRADE
- **Trending market**: ADX > 25 with clear BOS series — DO NOT fade the trend
